{"tid":935982,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實，改一個英文名真係咁難？","createTime":"2018-12-10T12:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T13:29:38.000Z","uid":57405,"like":6,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eb9accdd0c4d08b4d1bbb87a87fdd27075577339","tid":935982,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:10:42.000Z","msg":"身為公司一隻IT狗，要幫D員工開AC家常便飯，入個名，求其set個密碼比佢自己改，本來係一件好平常既事。<br />\n只不過近排好多新入職既同事，問佢地拎名開AC，問埋佢地有冇英文名，就求求其其比佢個英文拼音其中一個字我就算。例如叫阿「庭」既，就話叫佢阿「Ting」；姓「蔡」既，就話叫佢阿「Choi」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;&hellip;<br />\n真係「Choi」個你！而家你地做緊國際公司呀！公司文件全部英文，開會又要會英文（大部份董事係鬼佬），有時幫佢地整會議錄音，聽到班鬼佬講極都講唔出呢D所謂「英文名」真係哭笑不得&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n仲話自己香港人有幾崇洋，連一個正正常常既英文名都改唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaca8bbf484ba4b9814ecf43062edbe0d1f49099","tid":935982,"uid":1767,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"自豪自己個名有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n李嘉誠都無英文名"},{"pid":"dca0c96ec8fd59ca57338eff835c24be1e30dfc0","tid":935982,"uid":107219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"Hi, my name is dick （迪）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5316af6f8e76f1076e2b08ae011a3cd14ee7f2ce","tid":935982,"uid":57405,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dca0c96ec8fd59ca57338eff835c24be1e30dfc0","tid":935982,"uid":107219,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"Hi, my name is dick （迪